The paper discusses the development of intelligent virtual characters, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed tool involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The tool also aims to improve the authoring process by identifying missing information, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the iterative suggestion process involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
